content: Dear White, Purple seeks your support and cooperation in countering Orange's aggression. Let us stand together to protect our shared values of democracy and international law. Together, we can defend our territories and promote peace in the region.
We stand with you in this conflict against Orange. We condemn their aggressive assault and offer any assistance you may require. Together, we will prevail against this threat.

Purple strongly condemns Orange's aggressive assault on our territory. We urge all nations to stand against this act of aggression and support us in defending our sovereignty and protecting international peace and security.
